dcterms:creator: P. Bestagini
S. Milani
M. Tagliasacchi
S. Tubaro
dcterms:description: A dataset containing video sequences used for local tampering detection in video sequences, specifically designed for evaluating video forgery localization frameworks.
dcterms:title: REWIND dataset

dcterms:description: A set of encoded videos used in the experiments, but not explicitly referenced in the paper.
dcterms:title: D (set of encoded videos)

dcterms:description: A dataset of temporally-spliced videos created for the purpose of evaluating temporal splicing localization.
dcterms:title: Dtemp (temporally-spliced videos)

dcterms:description: A dataset of spatially-spliced videos created for the purpose of evaluating spatial splicing localization.
dcterms:title: Dspat (spatially-spliced videos)

dcterms:description: A training dataset consisting of 300 high-resolution videos used for training the CNN models.
dcterms:title: Training dataset of 300 high-resolution videos

dcterms:description: A testing dataset consisting of 1672 low-resolution videos used for testing the CNN models.
dcterms:title: Testing dataset of 1672 low-resolution videos

dcterms:description: A dataset of 300 high-resolution videos used for validation of the CNN models.
dcterms:title: Dataset of 300 high-resolution videos for validation

dcterms:description: A dataset of 60 encoded videos used for the dataset D.
dcterms:title: Dataset of 60 encoded videos (for dataset D)

dcterms:description: A dataset of 330 temporally-spliced videos created for the purpose of evaluating temporal splicing localization.
dcterms:title: Dataset of 330 temporally-spliced videos (Dtemp)

dcterms:description: A dataset of 330 spatially-spliced videos created for the purpose of evaluating spatial splicing localization.
dcterms:title: Dataset of 330 spatially-spliced videos (Dspat)
